ADVANCED FEATURES

-Filter search-       SEARCH
The search module lets you combine the different search options.
Enter the criteria successively as search parameters for the clue by
including | in the search command or by selecting FILTER from menu.

-Complement search-   SEARCH
Any of the searches can work in the complement mode as well.
This is specified by including  `!' in the search command.
Example:   !POST#  extracts word which do not have POST as substrings

-Symmetry-            GRID EDITOR
Blocking can be made symmetrical starting from each corner.
Switch between 2-Way, 4-Way and no symmetry
The Symmetry mode is changed by pressing CTRL-S during editing.





